harf chief executive officer the bank of new york mellon corporation charles scharf is the chief executive officer at the bank of new york mellon corporation scharf served as chief executive officer and a director of visa inc the world’s largest consumer payment system from november  to november  before joining visa scharf was a managing director of one equity partners the private investment arm of jpmorgan chase  co previously he served as chief executive officer of retail financial services at jpmorgan chase  co from  to  and as chief executive officer of the retail division of bank one corp from  to  scharf also served as chief financial officer of bank one corp from  to  chief financial officer of the global corporate and investment bank division at citigroup from  to  and chief financial officer of salomon smith barney and its predecessor company from  to  scharf joined the microsoft board of directors in october  he also serves on the board of visa and is a member of the board of trustees of johns hopkins university he holds a bachelor’s degree from johns hopkins university and a master of business administration degree from new york university back to top photos download photos of charles w scharf webjpg  printjpg follow us follow msftnews share this page tweet leadership  news center skip to main content try microsoft edge a fast and secure browser thats designed for windows  no thanks get started microsoft news center no results   items in shopping cart news center leadership find photos biographies and speech transcripts of microsoft executives and board of directors members press contact we communicationsmicrosoft media relations  senior leaders board members executive speeches senior leaders satya nadella chief executive officer judson althoff executive vice president worldwide commercial business chris capossela chief marketing officer and executive vice president marketing and consumer business jeanphilippe courtois executive vice president and preside