ncement is the culmination of the board of directors robust and longterm succession planning process charlie is an accomplished and distinguished leader with a record of profitably growing businesses driving innovation and managing complex largescale global financial services organizations scharf was most recently chief executive officer and a director of visa inc from october  till december  and was recognized for transforming the firm into a technologydriven digital commerce company gain access to more news your email address will remain confidential  privacy policy this article is not available as part of our free news service upgrade to a premium subscription or log in with an upgraded account find out more this site like many others uses small files called cookies to customize your experience cookies appear to be blocked on this browser please consider allowing cookies so that you can enjoy more content across globalcustodynet how do i enable cookies in my browser internet explorer  click the tools button or press alt and t on the keyboard and then click internet options  click the privacy tab  move the slider away from block all cookies to a setting youre comfortable with firefox  at the top of the firefox window click on the tools menu and select options  select the privacy panel  set firefox will to use custom settings for history  make sure accept cookies from sites is selected safari browser  click safari icon in menu bar  click preferences gear icon  click security icon  accept cookies select radio button only from sites i visit chrome  click the menu icon to the right of the address bar looks like  lines  click settings  click the show advanced settings tab at the bottom  click the content settings button in the privacy section  at the top under cookies make sure it is set to allow local data to be set recommended opera  click the red o button in the upper left hand corner  select settings  preferences  select the advanced tab  select cookies in the list